                <div class="jonra" data-uuid="cc46ea0f466b418c960f59a1f0c5a8df">
                    <h2 data-uuid="e3277941ae7f40338ea686a84d816a2e">The Rise of Television</h2>
                    <p class="source" data-uuid="c7bf6de5c1bf4ae7a85d3f59549660f6">In the 1940s very few American households had
                        televisions. This changed as incomes grew during the 1950s. The increased use
                        of televisions changed the way Americans accessed information and
                        entertainment.</p>
                </div>
